Dëkk baa ngi nekk ci wetu chutte yi, fi ndox mi di walee te moo tax ñu bari diko siyaare, nekk na barab bu touriste yi taamu lool, ndax barina fu nit mën dem ngir gis lu bees wala féexal xolam.
Dafa am ay mbir yu bari yi ngeen wara bayyi xel laata ak ci jamono ji ngeen di tukki.
Wàllum tukkikat yi ñu baña sàcc, ñu baña dugg wala bokk ci lépp luy jëflante gu leerul wala gu yoon di tere, warul yalwaan te warul teg kenn xel.
